\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Post-AI shock. The pre-AI wage $p_0(i)$ (dashed blue) is compared against the post-AI wage $p_1(i)$ (solid green). Below $I^*$, AI adds supply $s(i)>0$; the denominator in~\eqref  {eq:wage_postai} grows faster than the numerator, so wages fall. Above $I^*$, $s=0$ and workers benefit from the economy's higher output $\bar  Y > Y_0$. The upward slope of $p_0(i)$ is assumed for illustration only.}}{7}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:postai}{{2}{7}{Post-AI shock. The pre-AI wage $p_0(i)$ (dashed blue) is compared against the post-AI wage $p_1(i)$ (solid green). Below $I^*$, AI adds supply $s(i)>0$; the denominator in~\eqref {eq:wage_postai} grows faster than the numerator, so wages fall. Above $I^*$, $s=0$ and workers benefit from the economy's higher output $\bar Y > Y_0$. The upward slope of $p_0(i)$ is assumed for illustration only}{figure.2}{}}
